00:03:39.620 --> 00:03:41.419
And those are comments we can agree with.

00:03:42.620 --> 00:03:46.919
Our second question is, what do these words mean? They will become one flesh.

00:03:47.719 --> 00:04:01.719
Well, of course, the one flesh relationship certainly involves sexual union, but it goes beyond that because it includes a husband and wife who have achieved mental, emotional and spiritual harmony.

00:04:02.419 --> 00:04:06.419
They are to have a oneness in their purpose and desires.

00:04:06.919 --> 00:04:14.419
As Bible translator William Barclay renders it at Matthew 19, five, the husband will be joined inseparably to his wife.

00:04:15.219 --> 00:04:21.220
