00:04:31.720 --> 00:04:39.220
So when single people marry, they need to shift their thinking from mine to ours, from me to we.

00:04:39.920 --> 00:04:45.620
And so they must stop being single at heart and come to be married at heart, not just on paper.

00:04:46.620 --> 00:04:49.819
Our third question is, how can we show that we believe these words?

00:04:50.620 --> 00:05:00.420
