00:07:44.240 --> 00:07:53.439
And surely it was a time spent together in Christian activities that kept their marriage on a high spiritual plane working side by side to further the kingdom work.

00:07:54.439 --> 00:08:00.139
Now you and your marriage may be a part for much of the day due to different work and responsibilities.

00:08:00.639 --> 00:08:13.540
But can you find time each day to eat meals together to do household chores together to take walks together to be together to get caught up on what has gone on in your lives during the day.

00:08:14.639 --> 00:08:24.839
Aquila and Priscilla prove that being united in activities related to true worship can keep a couple's thinking and goals aligned and that does strengthen a marriage.

00:08:25.540 --> 00:08:35.539
For example, studying together, participating in congregation meetings together, sharing in the ministry together, praying together, in doing all of that.

00:08:36.539 --> 00:08:51.940
A person's interests, priorities and habits will harmonize with those of one spouse until like Aquila and Priscilla, we increasingly think, feel and act as one flesh.

00:08:52.639 --> 00:09:01.139
